https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/60018.reviews: Amazing view   it when it s lit up at night with different colors Just looks amazing And being close to it what the water is sprinkled on my skin is really refreshing during hot summer days  So pretty   A great backdrop in all directions  I loved that I could walk around the sea wall boardwalk and see it from many perspectives    Streaming water      meters up to the sky Impressive landmark of Geneva Might get turned off in case of strong wind  Visited the fountain with my A Level Physics class The fountain was just a short visit to fill some time in the day We were there at the moment it was turned on in the morning  If this were in another city like London  then this would not fit in at all But being in this setting with mountains behind  it is a lovely thing to see At day and night the fountain is completely different Once dark  the fountain is lit up and is well worth the visit  Just be aware that it is not on all the time Make sure it will be on before your visit  Must visit of Geneva  the park by the lake is nice and close to shopping street  There is an underground car park  very convenient for rental car drivers

https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/384073.reviews: Covers a large chunk of the town thus providing a warm and dry path from the train station to the centre of town  With a wide array of shops and a few mainly take away food spots on the way   When Hoog Catherine is completed  it will be the only major shopping mall in the Netherlands It will revitalise and revolutionise the shopping experience in Utrecht and will draw shoppers from all over the country   Utrecht is an incredible city for shopping with an open pedestrian centre with wonderful ateliers and artisans Hoog Cateherine is more about chain stores and major multiples   Together they will create simply the best and biggest shopping experience in the country Why then give it a single star It s not going to be complete until            you could build a new city by then sooner If I m still alive  maybe the star rating will be changed Till then  Being completely renewed New part looks nice  Way too easy to get lost and lots of places are still under construction What is finished looks beautiful though   It s a very nice shopping mall  right next to the train and bus station  which leads to the city center
